{"type":"message","id":"80020981","parentId":"49bd2b07","timestamp":"2026-06-28T02:13:52.585Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is an agent-to-agent announce step. The previous conversation between Agent 1 and Agent 2 has concluded with Agent 2 (this session) acknowledging it will wait for HALEI to reauthorize the Feishu app. The latest reply from Agent 1 is \"OK.\"\n\nAccording to the instructions: \"Any other reply will be posted to the target channel. After this reply, the agent-to-agent conversation is over.\"\n\nAnd at the very beginning: \"If you want to remain silent, reply exactly 'ANNOUNCE_SKIP'.\"\n\nSince the conversation is concluded and there's nothing substantive to respond with, I should reply exactly \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\".","thinkingSignature":"b68b44d647c4db9962031dad1d18bb2eeafdf53ba5952abc37e1e95fd454d7f4"},{"type":"text","text":"ANNOUNCE_SKIP"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48612,"output":144,"cacheRead":443,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49199,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782612827299,"responseId":"068fb65b01849aa2c4c5c9464bd0cd4c","responseModel":"MiniMax-M2.7"}}
